A small gungame map i had a laugh on with my mates so decided to put it on fps
simple really a bridge with ladders eitherside and a rope in the middle  
weapons stashed throughout
some bushes to hide in
couple of vans and cars and some boxes
oh n a river
thats about it
and theres no buy zones by the way as its a gg map 
cheers have fun
